page.title: 10THE COUNTRYSIDE
page.content: Most of the block is covered by agricultural land,hedges,small woods, conservation areas,residential property and small business properties.On the farm land cereal crops and fruit trees abound with the usual wildlife that goes with them. Small mammals and birds can be seen often in the fields but to the casual observer not many larger animals.There are many wild flowers including a rare wild orchid which can be found in Hardwick.Residential devlopment has upset the natural balance to some extent.There are many conservation minded people in the area defending the countryside.
